      "1608999044c6d7b253": {
        "type": "custom-content",
        "blocks": {
          "1608999044c6d7b253-0": {
            "type": "text",
            "settings": {
              "title": "MEAT YOUR PASSION!",
              "text": "<p>Ding Ding Ding -It’s Dinner time! At Carnivore House, we believe that <strong>every good meal begins with a great meat!</strong> Whether it’s a slow-braised beef brisket or juicy lamb chops grilled to perfection, we know that using superior ingredients is the secret to a mouthwatering meal. So we offer clean, healthy, locally-raised meat and poultry for the<strong> freshest, most delicious meat possible.</strong> Every animal is <strong>hand-picked at harvest time</strong> and humanely finished, with Zabihah Halal certification agents on-site to approve processing. </p>",
              "width": "50%",
              "alignment": "top-middle",
              "align_text": "left"
            }
          },
          "f9484238-855f-40e1-b171-b7454471855c": {
            "type": "text",
            "settings": {
              "title": "BUT WE GO BEYOND THAT. ",
              "text": "<p>We feel that every meal should be guilt-free and we know that good meat starts on the farm. So, we only work with local farms in the Pacific Northwest that meet the highest standards of our faith, ensuring each animal is raised well, fed a healthy natural halal diet, and treated with kindness and compassion from start to finish.  <br/><br/>At Carnivore House, we know finding the right cut of meat can be hard in a traditional halal butcher’s shop, so we offer premium gourmet cuts, smoked sausages seasoned to perfection, delicious deli meats and tender, flavor-packed jerky that will satisfy all your carnivore-cravings.  </p><p>With Carnivore House, you can dine the way you’ve always wanted to, completely guilt-free.  </p><p>We invite you to treat yourself and your family to the very BEST Zabihah Halal has to offer. Join us at Carnivore House and <em>meat your passion!</em> </p>",
              "width": "50%",
              "alignment": "top-middle",
              "align_text": "left"
            }
          },
          "dccb4968-2176-45e8-9885-22fcd863e7a8": {
            "type": "html",
            "settings": {
              "code": "<div style=\"text-align: center\"><a class=\"btn\" href=\"https://carnivorehouse.com/pages/about-us\">read more</a></div>",
              "width": "100%"
            }
          }
        },
